io.requery.async

Class CompletableEntityStore<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.requery.async.CompletableEntityStore<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - entity base type. See EntityStore.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompletionStageEntityStore<T>, EntityStore<T,CompletionStage<?>>, Queryable<T>, AutoCloseable

    public class CompletableEntityStore<T>
extends Object
implements CompletionStageEntityStore<T>
    Implementation of CompletionStageEntityStore where all operations are passed through a BlockingEntityStore instance. All operations are supplied via the given Executor.
